OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782231548
OL,3,CPeter Murrell sentenced to five years
OL,4,Cfor embezzling #400k of SNP funds
OL,6,FFormer SNP chief executive Peter
OL,7,FMurrell has been sentenced to five
OL,8,Fyears and three months in prison,
OL,9,Fafter he admitted to embezzling more
OL,10,Fthan #400,000 from the party.
OL,12,FMurrell - the estranged husband of
OL,13,FNicola Sturgeon - used the funds to
OL,14,Fmake hundreds of extravagant
OL,15,Fpurchases, including a #124,550
OL,16,Fmotorhome, cars, jewellery, luxury
OL,17,Fhomewares and designer stationery.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
