PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782231548
OL,3,CPeter Murrell sentenced to five years
OL,4,Cfor embezzling #400k of SNP funds
OL,6,FThe 61-year-old also falsified
OL,7,Faccounting records and created fake
OL,8,Finvoices in a bid to cover up his
OL,9,Fwrongdoing.
OL,11,FIn his sentencing remarks, Lord Young
OL,12,Ftold Murrell he had committed a
OL,13,F"calculated crime of dishonesty",
OL,14,Fadding that the offending increased in
OL,15,Ffrequency and amount over time.
OL,17,FHe said: "You found yourself unable to
OL,18,Fstop this offending, and it was only
OL,19,Fthe detection of the crime that
OL,20,Fbrought it to an end."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
