FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782231548
OL,3,CPeter Murrell sentenced to five years
OL,4,Cfor embezzling #400k of SNP funds
OL,6,FLast month, Murrell pleaded guilty to
OL,7,Fembezzling a total of #400,310.65 over
OL,8,Fa 12-year period between August 2010
OL,9,Fand October 2022.
OL,11,FThe court previously heard how
OL,12,FMurrell's role enabled him to make
OL,13,Fdirect transfers of cash from the
OL,14,Fparty's main bank account, which held
OL,15,Ffunds from "membership fees and
OL,16,Fdonations paid by party members and
OL,17,Fother donors and legacies".
OL,19,FMurrell also used multiple party
OL,20,F"charge cards", as well as making a
OL,21,Fnumber of false expense claims.
OL,26,@wD@LOUyD@ZO]|D@AOU|D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
