PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782231548
OL,3,CPeter Murrell sentenced to five years
OL,4,Cfor embezzling #400k of SNP funds
OL,6,FHe tried to dodge suspicion by giving
OL,7,Fhis purchases "misleading descriptions
OL,8,Fand/or accounting codes" in the
OL,9,Fparty's finance system, to which he
OL,10,Fhad direct access.
OL,12,FThe court heard a robotic lawnmower,
OL,13,Fwhich was purchased by Murrell for
OL,14,F#3,070, was misdescribed as "legal
OL,15,Ffees" in the SNP's accounting software.
OL,17,FA silver wine coaster worth #3,500 was
OL,18,Fdescribed as "leadership expenses".
OL,26,@oD@OOUpD@XO]vD@]OUwD@EO]zD@NOUzD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
