CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782231548
OL,3,CPeter Murrell sentenced to five years
OL,4,Cfor embezzling #400k of SNP funds
OL,6,FFollowing his sentencing, authorities
OL,7,Fhave released a series of police
OL,8,Finterviews where Murrell is questioned
OL,9,Fabout his purchase of #19,000 worth of
OL,10,Fpens, as well as pictures of some of
OL,11,Fthe other items.
OL,13,F'It is quite frankly an outrageous
OL,14,Famount of money to spend on pens in my
OL,15,Fopinion, what about your opinion?':
OL,16,FPolice asked Peter Murrell when
OL,17,Fquestioning the #19,000 he spent on
OL,18,Fpens using SNP money
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
