FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782231548
OL,3,CPeter Murrell sentenced to five years
OL,4,Cfor embezzling #400k of SNP funds
OL,6,FThe SNP party has said it will seek to
OL,7,Frecoup the money embezzled by Murrell
OL,8,F- but First Minister John Swinney said
OL,9,Fearlier this month that it would be
OL,10,Ffor a court to decide if Murrell's ex-
OL,11,Fwife, Nicola Sturgeon, had to return
OL,12,Fgifts.
OL,14,FMurrell's guilty plea led to intense
OL,15,Fscrutiny for the former first
OL,16,Fminister, who has denied knowledge of
OL,17,Fhis crimes, saying she was "deceived,
OL,18,Fmisled and betrayed".
OL,26,@yD@\OUzD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
