OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782231548
OL,3,CPeter Murrell sentenced to five years
OL,4,Cfor embezzling #400k of SNP funds
OL,6,FSturgeon was arrested and questioned
OL,7,Fas part of the police investigation
OL,8,Finto the SNP's finances, which was
OL,9,Fknown as Operation Branchform, but
OL,10,FPolice Scotland confirmed she would
OL,11,Fface no action.
OL,13,FIn a statement released following
OL,14,FMurrell's sentencing, Sturgeon's
OL,15,Flawyer Aamer Anwar said: "Ms Sturgeon
OL,16,Fremains angry, hurt and distressed
OL,17,Fabout the devastating impact of Mr
OL,18,FMurrell's actions on her, his family,
OL,19,Ffriends and the SNP.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
