OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782231548
OL,3,CPeter Murrell sentenced to five years
OL,4,Cfor embezzling #400k of SNP funds
OL,6,F"Ms Sturgeon was utterly deceived and
OL,7,Flet down by her husband, whom she had
OL,8,Ftrusted. Why he acted as he did will
OL,9,Falways be beyond her comprehension.
OL,10,FShe is utterly appalled that he did so
OL,11,Fand will never understand why."
